  • Constructor Details

    • Turno

      public Turno(String designacao, List<String> turmasList, String numeroInscritos, List<String> cursosList)
      Creates a new instance of the Turno class with the specified designation, list of turmas (class groups), number of enrolled students, and list of cursos (courses).
      Parameters:
      designacao - a string representing the designation of the turno.
      turmasList - a list of strings representing the turmas (class groups) associated with the turno.
      numeroInscritos - a string representing the number of enrolled students in the turno.
      cursosList - a list of strings representing the cursos (courses) associated with the turno.
